tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE leadership_project_milestones (
    milestone_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    project_name VARCHAR(255),
    milestone VARCHAR(255),
    outcome TEXT,
    completion_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE leadership_projects (
    project_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    project_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    start_date DATE NOT NULL,
    end_date DATE NOT NULL,
    leader_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE project_outcomes (
    outcome_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    project_id INT NOT NULL,
    outcome_description TEXT,
    outcome_date DATE,
    FOREIGN KEY (project_id) REFERENCES leadership_projects(project_id)
);

CREATE TABLE ProjectMilestones (
    milestone_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    project_id INT,
    milestone_name VARCHAR(255),
    milestone_date DATE,
    completed BOOLEAN
);

CREATE TABLE PerformanceEvaluation (
    eval_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    project_id INT,
    milestone_id INT,
    employee_id INT,
    rating INT
);

CREATE TABLE leadership_projects (
  project_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  project_name TEXT,
  start_date DATE,
  end_date DATE,
  leader_id INT,
  outcome TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE project_participants (
  participant_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  participant_name TEXT,
  project_id INT,
  role TEXT,
  hours_worked INT
)

CREATE TABLE project_milestones (
  milestone_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  milestone_name TEXT,
  project_id INT,
  milestone_date DATE,
  completion_status TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE performance_evaluation (
  evaluation_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  participant_id INT,
  milestone_id INT,
  leadership_rating INT,
  comments TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE projects (
    project_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    project_name VARCHAR(255),
    project_description TEXT,
    project_leader VARCHAR(100),
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE milestones (
    milestone_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    project_id INT,
    milestone_name VARCHAR(255),
    milestone_description TEXT,
    deadline_date DATE,
    completed_date DATE,
    FOREIGN KEY (project_id) REFERENCES projects(project_id)
);

CREATE TABLE outcomes (
    outcome_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    project_id INT,
    milestone_id INT,
    outcome_description TEXT,
    outcome_date DATE,
    FOREIGN KEY (project_id) REFERENCES projects(project_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (milestone_id) REFERENCES milestones(milestone_id)
);

CREATE TABLE evaluations (
    evaluation_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    project_id INT,
    evaluator_id INT,
    evaluation_date DATE,
    evaluation_comments TEXT,
    FOREIGN KEY (project_id) REFERENCES projects(project_id)
);
